{"tid":1556111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[記者滅聲]國際記者EJIBLINKS OFOEGBU聲稱警方試圖賄賂他不要引起美國白宮關注","createTime":"2019-09-09T15:08:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T14:27:54.000Z","uid":269202,"like":98,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"a036c7f617926475c4ae539d17ef0e99b64250dd","tid":1556111,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:08:44.000Z","msg":"頭盔：以下所有警方或警察字眼都不是指控警方，只是疑似是警方<br />\nEJIBLINKS OFOEGBU的twitter上自稱是國際記者，Blogger和人權活動家，也是攝影師。<br />\n<br />\n他在twitter上貼上whatsapp 對話，有自稱是香港警察是人<br />\n向他提出邀請他見證抗爭者的暴力，並且說會付他的ticket<br />\n<blockquote>I will pay for your ticket to fly over the HK and see how violet these people are.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n於是EJIBLINKS OFOEGBU就認為警方嘗試賄賂他<br />\n後來還說因為記者常常在twitter上引起白宮注意，令警察收到不少相關電郵<br />\n希望他能停止twitter,下面附上連結<br />\n內有對話whatsapp 截圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ejikeofoegbu1/status/1170934958237650944?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fejikeofoegbu1%2Fstatus%2F1170934958237650944%3Fs%3D20&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNkPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=fc05f321\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fejikeofoegbu1%2Fstatus%2F1170934958237650944%3Fs%3D20&h=ebc59281\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ejikeofoegbu1/status/1170934958237650944?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n重點引述：<br />\n1. 警方掌握外媒的電話號碼及twitter動向<br />\n2. 疑似警方用whatsapp這種方法去個別接觸傳媒<br />\n3. 警方希望透過展示所謂抗爭者暴力一面，要求記者不要再在twitter上引起美國白宮注意<br />\n4. 警方希望付記者的機票 ／ 直升機票錢可以作為願意出來見面的禮儀或其他只有他們明白的意思<br />\n5. 警方告訴記者，你說的不是事實。<br />\n6. 並且這位警察聲稱自已在現場，見證抗爭者暴力，警察沒有警暴，奇怪是他同時兼任聯絡記者及在示威現場的工作, 他是什麼工作崗位？？？？看來必定是經理級"},{"pid":"601d9db4d7d72cc8535857ed72feeeb981af5437","tid":1556111,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:09:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}